Interface IIterativeModel<T>

This is an example interface to extend the functionality of a model.

Here we are going to add more requirements for a model, in this case so that it can handle iteration.

In your Model Systems you can then have a field of type "IIterationModel" and then only models that provide this interface can be loaded into it by XTMF.
